Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.44,0:00:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要走著去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.39,0:00:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去那有著各種各樣的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.85,0:00:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既溫暖又快樂的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.09,0:00:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想這麼做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.13,0:00:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.05,0:00:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.08,0:01:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 媽媽 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.67,0:01:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.39,0:01:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.68,0:01:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.37,0:01:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.39,0:01:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.45,0:01:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪我玩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.63,0:02:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和早苗阿姨是怎麼玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.45,0:02:04.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讀書
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.97,0:02:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼有帶書來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.86,0:02:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和大叔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.38,0:02:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.72,0:02:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棒球？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.75,0:02:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.01,0:02:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駒田
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.01,0:02:19.65,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駒田德廣：日本著名棒球運動員，擁有滿壘男的稱號
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.25,0:02:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模仿秀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.89,0:02:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.98,0:02:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.84,0:02:27.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.74,0:02:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔到底教了些什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.52,0:02:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 媽媽你聽我說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.33,0:02:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 好好坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.14,0:02:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 媽媽 媽媽聽我說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.00,0:02:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣吵吵鬧鬧地多羞人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.20,0:02:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為媽媽你不聽我說嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.70,0:02:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.05,0:02:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微考慮一下周圍的人好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.65,0:02:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.53,0:02:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.74,0:02:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.64,0:02:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.51,0:03:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑哪去了 那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.07,0:03:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.15,0:03:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊 想上廁所的話先說一聲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:14.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.08,0:03:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別騙人了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.41,0:03:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…說不可以哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰說的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.34,0:03:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎 那個人竟會這麼嚴格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.09,0:03:35.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也有可以哭的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.42,0:03:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊 在廁所裏哭的話就不會有人注意到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.94,0:03:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想哭的時候就哭 有什麼不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.74,0:03:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在好好哭一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:03:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想哭的時候卻不能哭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.72,0:04:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長大後這種情況少不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.71,0:04:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要玩具嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.45,0:04:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選一個吧 我給你買
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.63,0:04:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.26,0:04:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.23,0:04:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.91,0:04:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別勉強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.22,0:04:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.33,0:04:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是買個適合女孩子的比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.28,0:04:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.11,0:04:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.66,0:04:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的興趣也挺奇怪的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.30,0:04:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 玩你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.09,0:04:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能成為一個快樂的暑假嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能呢 和我這樣的人一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.30,0:05:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.18,0:05:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.20,0:05:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路黑小心一點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.46,0:05:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.95,0:05:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.43,0:05:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.84,0:05:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次又怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.26,0:05:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.17,0:05:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢火蟲 難道不認識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.90,0:05:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次見到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.54,0:05:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊的比較晚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.74,0:06:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.60,0:06:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.91,0:06:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我臉上有什麼東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.12,0:06:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就別這樣盯著人家的臉看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.92,0:06:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼話想說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.82,0:06:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.00,0:06:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在害怕我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 說說看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.76,0:06:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再大聲吼了的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我媽媽的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:34.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去問早苗阿姨去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.21,0:06:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問她 她不告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.28,0:06:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才來問我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.71,0:06:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去問早苗阿姨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就說我不願意和你說這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.67,0:07:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.43,0:07:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.98,0:07:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.76,0:07:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 把帽子戴好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要走不少路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.95,0:07:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.43,0:07:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.11,0:07:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想看得更清楚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.58,0:07:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.08,0:07:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 把腳分開
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.14,0:07:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真輕啊 你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.85,0:07:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.55,0:08:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.27,0:08:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.77,0:08:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跑太遠哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.73,0:08:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之是來對了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.52,0:08:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.69,0:08:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.86,0:08:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.01,0:08:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就只是在這附近玩的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明沒有跑多遠的啊 真是奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:08:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐 算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:09:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去的時候再給你買個一樣的 好不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.67,0:09:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到的話也沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.96,0:09:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也真固執呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.11,0:09:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.07,0:09:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到那邊去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別走開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.80,0:09:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.72,0:10:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是岡崎朋也吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.40,0:10:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.98,0:10:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問… 您認識我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我當然知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.54,0:10:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是岡崎史乃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.16,0:10:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡崎…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.38,0:10:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是你父親 岡崎直幸的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一位叫古河的人聯絡我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.48,0:10:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是在這裏就能等到你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是早苗阿姨嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.97,0:10:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經長這麼大了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.28,0:10:50.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前有和您見過面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.93,0:10:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你還很小的時候 在這裏見過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.57,0:10:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在你母親敦子過世之後的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直幸還在贖罪中嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.92,0:11:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 應該已經出獄回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.05,0:11:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這段回憶想必非常痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.10,0:11:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子以前並不是這麼蠢的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.59,0:11:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時敦子和直幸都還是學生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.60,0:11:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然周圍的人都反對他們結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.05,0:11:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過直幸依然從高中退學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.59,0:11:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一間狹小的公寓裏開始了兩人的生活…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.95,0:11:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但當時 真的很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.49,0:11:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守護著自己所愛的人而生活著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.25,0:11:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅如此 那孩子就已經很幸福了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.39,0:11:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久之後 敦子的腹中有了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.33,0:11:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在小小的祝福之中 你誕生了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.89,0:12:08.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這份幸福沒能持續多久
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.14,0:12:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敦子因車禍而過世
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.43,0:12:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於那孩子來說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.58,0:12:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是無法再振作起來的變故
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.29,0:12:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 還不能就此絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.15,0:12:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為當時還有年幼的你在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.80,0:12:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「一定要親手把這個孩子撫養成人」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.42,0:12:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那一天 從這個地方開始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.77,0:12:52.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直幸就緊牽著你的手 開始了旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.99,0:13:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那以後的日子是那孩子一生中最努力的時期
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無數次被辭退 輾轉奔波
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 也從未鬆開過你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.98,0:13:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用僅有的一點錢給你買玩具 讓你吃零食
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.35,0:13:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為你犧牲了自己所有的運氣和成功的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.87,0:13:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管有時候對你會很嚴格 很粗暴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.47,0:13:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這一切都是為了能把你好好撫養成人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.67,0:13:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 對於直幸來說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.46,0:13:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是非常辛苦的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.65,0:13:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了排遣工作上的辛酸 他開始借酒消愁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.91,0:13:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝醉了之後對你動粗的事情也有過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.87,0:13:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 那孩子還是選擇和你一起生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.71,0:14:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 當你到了能自己決定自己人生的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直幸已經失去了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.29,0:14:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作 信賴 運氣 朋友 所有一切都沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你現在的情況和當時的直幸很像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是很痛苦的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.49,0:14:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但正因為如此 我才想把這番話告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.10,0:14:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能知道直幸是一個怎樣的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.35,0:14:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經常買零食給我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.00,0:14:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手牽著手去散步
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.46,0:14:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為什麼會忘記了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也 你認為直幸是個不稱職的父親嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.03,0:14:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:14:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才是比他更不稱職的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.38,0:15:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和那一天的老爸處在相同的境況中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.44,0:15:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在的我卻那麼軟弱 那麼沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.99,0:15:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那麼軟弱 那麼不中用 那麼沒出息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.59,0:15:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此 依然為自己的孩子竭盡了所能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.80,0:15:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為那孩子感到自豪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為一個人 他也許有很多失敗的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但作為父親 他非常了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.69,0:15:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.74,0:15:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼認為的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太感謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.07,0:15:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 這下就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.84,0:16:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋也
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.25,0:16:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子實在是太過努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.75,0:16:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了該讓他休息一下的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.05,0:16:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你轉告直幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「快回來吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.38,0:16:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會在這片土地上等著那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.75,0:16:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.17,0:16:37.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.17,0:16:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 她叫汐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.55,0:16:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在找嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.48,0:16:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.42,0:16:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.57,0:17:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.48,0:17:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個機器人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能已經找不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.64,0:17:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是沒辦法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.48,0:17:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再給你買個新的吧 好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.17,0:17:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是獨一無二的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.28,0:17:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,商店裏不還有很多在賣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.56,0:17:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為我選 為我買的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.16,0:17:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爸爸第一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.08,0:17:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直很寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.46,0:17:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.42,0:17:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起來旅行 覺得開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.87,0:17:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.97,0:17:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.99,0:17:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.60,0:17:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以陪在你身邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.73,0:18:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然之前一直 很長一段時間都是個不稱職的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是從今以後會為了汐而努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.34,0:18:12.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以可以陪在你身邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.66,0:18:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.18,0:18:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.51,0:18:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你陪著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.70,0:18:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是今天失去了一個很重要的東西 所以很傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.22,0:18:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.53,0:18:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以不用忍著了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.16,0:18:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗說過
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.52,0:18:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能哭的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.74,0:18:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有爸爸的懷裏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.74,0:18:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.26,0:19:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.00,0:19:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.06,0:19:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.46,0:19:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.67,0:19:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 汐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.35,0:19:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想聽媽媽的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.41,0:19:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.71,0:19:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那就坐到這裏來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.82,0:19:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽啊 是個好像隨時都會哭出來的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.25,0:20:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次見到她的時候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.26,0:20:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那麼沒有自信 那麼軟弱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.55,0:20:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直呆站在學校的那條坡道下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:18.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 你知道她在坡道下說什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.05,0:20:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然閉著眼睛說「豆沙麵包」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.55,0:20:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是媽媽的習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說出自己想吃的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.92,0:20:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從而來讓自己鼓起勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.89,0:20:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早苗阿姨那個時候忙於工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.73,0:20:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾乎沒有給她做便當的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.09,0:20:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬去拜託的話 早苗阿姨肯定會擠出時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.65,0:20:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是媽媽並沒有那麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.35,0:20:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽就是這樣的一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.45,0:20:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.91,0:20:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.47,0:20:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後啊 媽媽她…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.35,0:21:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.61,0:21:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.41,0:21:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.25,0:21:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼連你也哭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.37,0:21:31.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 因為回憶起了媽媽的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.50,0:21:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 我們繼續說下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.68,0:21:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽她那時想要演舞台劇
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.65,0:21:46.03,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道什麼叫演舞台劇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.25,0:21:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚 我找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.21,0:21:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.29,0:21:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我能守護的東西
